main event: A person observed a moored UFO over Freeville, New York for about 18.7 minutes on August 9, 1968.
interesting points: The witness was described as clear-headed.
The UFO was estimated to be 18.0 feet in size.
The camera aperture setting was f/5.6.
There was amplification and reduction of the UFO's brightness, but no change in brightness of 90 degrees.
The UFO was observed to be vertical with radar at 90 degrees.
